### Syntax definition
# Amber's parser uses Parsing Expression Grammer (PEG) 
#
# .     : any character
# P*    : zero or many
# P+    : one or many
# P..   : sequence
# P / P : choice
# P?    : option
# &P    : and
# !P    : not
# (...) : grouping

